tender.title: WSCC DR - Public Health Services - AWARD
tender.description:
A contract for the provision of Public Health Services, as described in Documents 2a - g (Service Specification) ("the Contract") is being tendered by West Sussex County Council ("the Council") in accordance with the Light Touch Regime (LTR) of the Public Contracts Regulations 2015 (SI 2015/102) ("the 2015 Regulations"). 
      
      The aim of the procurement process is to establish an approved supplier list for Public Health Services in the County of West Sussex. As such, please note that bidders will not be competing with each other for a place on this contract. All bidders who pass the evaluation stage, as detailed in Parts 3 and 4 below will be offered a place on the approved supplier list. 
      
      The procurement process will be undertaken using the OJEU Open Procedure and will be divided into the following six lots: 
      
      Lot 1: NHS Health Check Services
      Lot 2: Smoking Cessation Services
      Lot 3: Alcohol Identification and Brief Advice Services
      Lot 4: Intrauterine Device Services
      Lot 5: Contraceptive Implant Services 
      Lot 6: Emergency Hormonal Contraception Services
